@startuml scaling_scale_down_client_paths
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultFontName "SansSerif"

title K_SCALE_DOWN / K_SCALING：错误如何回到客户端（典型路径）

== A. K_SCALE_DOWN：HealthCheck（客户端顶层可见） ==

actor "业务 / 运维" as APP
participant "KVClient / ObjectClient" as CLI
participant "ClientWorkerRemoteApi" as API
participant "Worker RPC Stub\n(自研 RPC 通道)" as STUB
participant "WorkerOCServiceImpl" as WK
participant "EtcdClusterManager" as ETCD

APP -> CLI : HealthCheck()
CLI -> API : HealthCheck(state)
API -> STUB : HealthCheck(opts, req, rsp)
STUB -> WK : HealthCheck RPC
WK -> ETCD : CheckLocalNodeIsExiting()
alt 节点正在退出
  ETCD --> WK : true
  WK --> STUB : Status K_SCALE_DOWN\nWorker is exiting now
else 正常
  ETCD --> WK : false
  WK --> STUB : OK
end
STUB --> API : 同上 Status
API --> CLI : 同上
CLI --> APP : Status 码 31 或 OK\n无 RetryOnError

== B. K_SCALING：MultiPublish 元数据（客户端会按码重试） ==

APP -> CLI : Set / MSet 等下沉到 MultiPublish
CLI -> API : MultiPublish(...)
loop RetryOnError 含 K_SCALING
  API -> STUB : MultiPublish RPC
  STUB -> WK : MultiPublish / CreateMultiMeta 链
  alt meta 仍在 moving 循环重试
    WK --> STUB : 继续等待 Master
  else moving 结束仍失败
    WK --> STUB : Status K_SCALING\nThe cluster is scaling...
  end
  STUB --> API : K_SCALING
  API -> API : 消耗预算重试
end
API --> CLI : 最终 OK 或耗尽超时等
note right of API
  仅 MultiPublish 把 K_SCALING\n列入重试集合
end note

== C. Get：last_rc 为 K_SCALING 时（不重试、顶层可能仍 OK） ==

APP -> CLI : Get
CLI -> API : Get(getParam, rsp, payloads)
loop RetryOnError 不含 K_SCALING
  API -> STUB : Get RPC
  STUB -> WK : Get
  WK --> STUB : RPC OK + rsp.last_rc\n可能含 32
  STUB --> API : stub OK
  API -> API : recvStatus = last_rc
  alt K_TRY_AGAIN 或 RPC 超时类或 OOM 全失败
    API --> API : return recvStatus 触发重试
  else last_rc == K_SCALING
    API --> API : return OK 结束 RetryOnError
  end
end
API --> CLI : 常返回顶层 OK\n错误可能在 objects 内
note right of CLI
  Access log 的 code 取决于\n上层是否把 per-object\n错误提升为 Status
end note

@enduml
